officesedit citadel employs more than  individuals globally with its flagship operation located in the citadel center a  million office tower in the heart of downtown chicago the story citadel center office tower opened in  with citadel as its anchor tenant citadel also has offices in new york hong kong san francisco boston dallas london houston greenwich denver shenzen shanghai and toronto philanthropyedit citadel is an active participant in the community by providing educational opportunities and helping children and families with acute medical needs the firm also partners with food banks around the united states for a virtual food drive in  citadels contributions to the greater chicago food depository were the highest from a single corporate donor in that organizations history citadel leads a business plan competition for the national foundation for teaching entrepreneurship mentoring low income high school students in january  citadel partnered with the national museum of mathematics momath to tutor prepare and support math and science students from low income communities recognitionedit citadel has been acknowledged through various awards and accolades in  citadel received a peoples pick award as one of the  great places to work in financial services the firm also ranked among the top  companies to work for according to employee surveys by great places to work in  in  institutional investoralpha magazine gave citadel an a grade and the  ranking among hedge funds worldwide in  citadel was named the best overall hedge fund group in the hedge funds reviews americas award institutional investor named citadel multistrategy hedge fund manager of the year in  and  and institutional hedge fund manager of the year in  see alsoedit kenneth c griffin the quants how a new breed of math whizzes conquered wall street and nearly destroyed it merrill lynch pierce fenner  smith inc v manning a  supreme court case involving naked short selling claims against citadel derivative g