are similar much has changed in our production methods yet we continue to improve not compromise our line of products our quality and our services for those of you who knew him at terrell you will be happy to know that jack knauss still comes by from time to time to inspect our work   insider trading  griffin kenneth c  form  sec filings home  archives  products  about  contact  faq  new user sign up  sign in form  filings insider buys significant buys penny stocksinsider buying insider sales insider buy sell ratios stock options insider tradingstock screener insider tradinggraph view insider watch sec filings insider trading  griffin kenneth c select time period  month  months  months  months  year  years  years  years all data       google     yahoo send this page to   blog    digg    reddit    facebook    stumble    delicious enter stock ticker symbol or cik cik lookup search by company or insider name insiders might sell their shares for any number of reasons but they buy them for only one they think the price will rise  peter lynch  what is insider trading email a friend  historical filings delayed by  months new user sign up for real time data existing user sign in common stock purchase or sale transactiondate reporteddate company symbol insiderrelationship sharestraded averageprice totalamount sharesowned filing purchase  pm great basin scientific inc gbsn citadel gp llccitadel securities llcgriffin kenneth c owner    indirect view sale  pm great basin scientific inc gbsn citadel gp llccitadel securities llcgriffin kenneth c owner    indirect view purchase  pm seritage growth properties srg citadel gp llcsurveyor capital ltdcitadel securities llccitadel advisors llccitadel advisors holdings iii lpgriffin kenneth c owner    indirect view sale  pm seritage growth properties srg citadel gp llcsurveyor capital ltdcitadel securities llccitadel advisors llccitadel advisors holdings iii lpgriffin kenneth c owner    indirect view purchase  pm seritage growth properti